data.description: Lovely home in sought after Braddock Place in Wylie that is FHA Assumable on a fixed 3.125 interest rate!!!  This home has it all, office with French doors, formal dining room, beautiful flooring, split bedrooms, laundry room with sink, and open floorplan just to name a few amenities to feast your eyes upon.  Fabulous kitchen with SS appliances, gas cook top, refrigerator, walk in pantry, large island and breakfast eating area.  Kitchen over looks spacious family room that has a FP and offers a great place for conversation and relaxation.  Find peace and tranquility in the huge primary suite with sitting area, huge walk-in closet, separate glass frame shower, and large garden tub. As you make your way upstairs there is a large game room for your enjoyment and entertaining plus a bedroom and bathroom.  Nice covered patio with pergola. Spacious backyard to entertain friends and family. Minutes from restaurants, shops, and Firewheel Mall.  This home is FHA Assumable - buyer must qualify.
